msgid ""
"If non-zero, hints at (or if **flags** has MAP_FIXED set, specifies) the "
"address at which to perform this mapping. See mmap (2) for details. Must be "
"page-aligned."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../core-api/mm-api:115: ../mm/mmap.c:316
msgid ""
